# AUTHORS

This file lists the individuals who hold copyright in the WatchTower
codebase. Contributions are licensed inbound under the same terms that
govern the directory they land in (Apache 2.0 outside `pro/`, Elastic
License 2.0 inside `pro/`). Each contributor retains copyright in their
own work; the project as a whole is collectively "The WatchTower Authors".

Add yourself by including a line in the same pull request that introduces
your first contribution:

    Name <email>           — first commit YYYY-MM-DD

Order is chronological by first contribution.

